`/newsyntax
#include <vcc.h>

_(def \integer f(\integer a)
  _(decreases a)
{
  if (a < 0)
    return 0;
  else
    return f(a - 1) + g(a, a + a);
})

_(def \integer g(\integer a, \integer b)
  _(decreases a, b)
{
  if (a < 0)
    return 0;
  else
    return f(a - 1) + (b < 0 ? 0 : g(a, b - 1));
})
`
Verification of f succeeded.
Verification of g succeeded.
`
